{"tid":1224281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"釋放所有示威者","createTime":"2019-06-15T02:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T02:52:33.000Z","uid":40855,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7004d4224e47b93358bcb7aaa43ae9e33b18f5c0","tid":1224281,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:49:03.000Z","msg":"遊行訴求要包括釋放同撤銷控告所有示威者，縱使和理非極唔認同衝擊行為，但如果無星期三嘅衝擊，三百萬人包圍政總都好，佢都會好似星期日噉照出聲明，聽到聲音，做法照舊。無論任何成果，星期三班衝擊者功不可抺，香港人要同佢哋同行。儘管佢哋係暴力，但呢個暴力都係以武制暴，用緊條命救香港。"},{"pid":"e83ba4551bb4b0b1d005be2acd77ff684f865fef","tid":1224281,"uid":109646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ckoFw6y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FckoFw6y.png&h=af3ffe1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e32d3f54c4974ad09467c6fc089391be4b847918","tid":1224281,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93cbbfffc21999a8a27d6b3f0bebbf79fa0a9232","tid":1224281,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590fb4e2811e6f716311b48f50f2aa2de15de2da","tid":1224281,"uid":37689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-1